t&amp;author=B+Taouli&amp;author=EE+Sigmund&amp;publication_year=2011&amp;journal=Invest+Radiol&amp;pages=285-291&amp;doi=10.1097%2FRLI.0b013e3181ffc485&amp;pmid=21102345">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">60.</div><div id="r60" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Rheinheimer S, Stieltjes B, Schneider F, et al. Investigation of renal lesions by diffusion-weighted magnetic resonance imaging applying intravoxel incoherent motion-derived parameters: initial experience. <em>Eur J Radiol</em> 2012;81(3):e310–e316.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ejrad.2011.10.016">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22104090/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Investigation+of+renal+lesions+by+diffusion-weighted+magnetic+resonance+imaging+applying+intravoxel+incoherent+motion-derived+parameters%3A+initial+experience&amp;author=S+Rheinheimer&amp;author=B+Stieltjes&amp;author=F+Schneider&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=Eur+J+Radiol&amp;pages=e310-e316&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.ejrad.2011.10.016&amp;pmid=22104090">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">61.</div><div id="r61" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Wang Z, Su MY, Nalcioglu O. Measurement of tumor vascular volume and mean microvascular random flow velocity magnitude by dynamic Gd-DTPA-albumin enhanced and diffusion-weighted MRI. <em>Magn Reson Med</em> 1998;40(3):397–404.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/mrm.1910400309">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9727942/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-sch